## 📌 Milestone 4: Dashboard Development & Insights

### 🎯 Objective
Build an interactive dashboard to visualize insights and support decision-making.

### 🛠️ Tools Used
- Power BI

### 📊 Dashboard Features
- KPI Cards:
  - Total Tickets
  - Open Tickets
  - SLA Compliance %
  - Average Resolution Time

- Interactive Filters:
  - Priority
  - Issue Type
  - Team
  - Date Range

- Visualizations:
  - Ticket Trends Over Time
  - Priority Distribution
  - SLA Compliance by Team
  - Resolution Time Analysis

### 💡 Key Insights Delivered
- Identification of SLA breaches
- Teams with high backlog
- High-impact issue categories
- Trends in ticket volume

### 🚀 Business Impact
- Improved visibility into IT operations
- Better decision-making for resource allocation
- Faster identification of bottlenecks

### ✅ Outcome
Fully functional dashboard enabling data-driven IT support management.
